body_html: @anhtu812 sometimes between different TF versions schema change and frozen graph needs to be updated. Did you freeze the graph with same tensorflow or are you loading it from a file saved by an earlier revision? If it is the second case, could you please try loading and saving frozen graph def to update it to current schema? If not, some fixes might have missed 1.10 cutoff and may require you to try master.
